{"tid":1378942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人願意罷工...直至政府回應？","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T17:47:13.000Z","uid":159169,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1157df5f2a7f3d8eedd33989b71b0460841de058","tid":1378942,"uid":159169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"罷工要齊心先會事成，而且唔單止需要我地一班恆常會遊行既手足，係需要當日果二百萬群眾，甚至更多，先會逼到政府正面回應我地既訴求。<br />\n罷工同時係講個信字，大家都好怕得自己罷，就寧願番左先，但如果長期罷工，只要一開始有一部分願意長期罷工，其他人見到就會開始加入。<br />\n兩個月黎每次都見到有手足受傷，黑警越黎越失性，其實再拖落去，我地贏既機會會越黎越細，賺錢重要，我都想賺多d，但香港冇左，幾多錢都番唔到黎，最弊仲要比中國接管到時有錢都冇命享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你願意罷工...直至政府回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一日當放下假，擺下姿態就算"},{"pid":"3085af094582980230d216414c87a81e044d0f82","tid":1378942,"uid":14262,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"我罷到失咗業了<br />\n<br />\n支持支持"},{"pid":"75aed1feeabc74e014a8b7bd64af62cd481a117e","tid":1378942,"uid":159169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"前線用緊佢條命去換取機會，換取香港未來<br />\n<br />\n我知全線罷工對一班中立既市民黎講犧牲都看似好大，但我地香港唔團結就冇人救到我地。<br />\n<br />\n今次要贏，今次要一齊贏"},{"pid":"afcbe8c56c59b0d287b02990b8bead67d67f9b1a","tid":1378942,"uid":22967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"05b923caef62c5bfb6ff976d2bd2b0177594f3c7","tid":1378942,"uid":154030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:16:51.000Z","msg":"罷工就全香港一齊罷<br />\n唔好咩730<br />\n一齊8月5<br />\n成效實大過分開罷"},{"pid":"9ea9caa006fa6d9be8e4505b649a55bf456e2f81","tid":1378942,"uid":265290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bb06c929c40787b4b2ee915e8d93d29d79fbcee","tid":1378942,"uid":159169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"見隔離post 話搞誓師大會等大家安心罷工，我覺得未嘗不可。而且如果聯絡到工會，大家會更加願意出黎"},{"pid":"c270805601feff9769a262cd88093200488af7a1","tid":1378942,"uid":292733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"【 有冇人覺得好無力 ？】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378949</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"caabf4dd9b2a58bdd87df454c8051efeaf985265","tid":1378942,"uid":159169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:27:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c3dafbb2d6c3fd6cf3468e548b9b8601af95695","tid":1378942,"uid":124452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e5e34042c5dcd8d4745c1444c3d3dc30df656665","tid":1378942,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c27f335332d01e98ada23ad28c6d9efab9e59eff","tid":1378942,"uid":159169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"push."}]}